                    "content": "<p>Charge on the capacitor is given by $Q = I \\alpha e^{\\frac{tI}{\\Delta V \\epsilon_0 \\beta}}$ where $\\alpha$ and $\\beta$ are constants. $t =$ time, $I =$ current, $\\Delta V =$ potential difference.</p> <p>Then dimensions of $\\frac{\\beta}{\\alpha}$ is same as the dimensions of</p>",
