                "question": {
                  "en": {
                    "comprehension": null,
                    "direction": null,
                    "content": "<p>An unknown quantity '<b>α</b>' is expressed as $\\alpha = \\dfrac{2ma}{\\beta} \\log\\left(1 + \\dfrac{2\\beta \\ell}{ma}\\right)$, where $m$ = mass, $a$ = acceleration, $\\ell$ = length. The unit of $\\alpha$ should be</p>",
                    "options": [
                      {
                        "identifier": "A",
                        "content": "<p>s<sup>−1</sup></p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "B",
                        "content": "<p>m/s</p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "C",
                        "content": "<p>m/s<sup>2</sup></p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "D",
                        "content": "<p>meter</p>"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "hi": {
                    "comprehension": null,
                    "direction": null,
                    "content": "<p>एक अज्ञात राशि '<b>α</b>' को $\\alpha = \\dfrac{2ma}{\\beta} \\log\\left(1 + \\dfrac{2\\beta \\ell}{ma}\\right)$ के रूप में व्यक्त किया गया है, जहाँ $m$ = द्रव्यमान, $a$ = त्वरण, $\\ell$ = लंबाई। $\\alpha$ का मात्रक होना चाहिए</p>",
                    "options": [
                      {
                        "identifier": "A",
                        "content": "<p>s<sup>−1</sup></p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "B",
                        "content": "<p>m/s</p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "C",
                        "content": "<p>m/s<sup>2</sup></p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "D",
                        "content": "<p>मीटर</p>"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                "subTopic": null,
                "subject": "physics",
                "timeAllotted": 90000,
                "topic": "dimensions-of-physical-quantities",
                "type": "mcq"
              },
