                "question": {
                  "en": {
                    "comprehension": null,
                    "direction": null,
                    "content": "<p>Given that $y = A \\sin\\left[\\frac{2 \\pi}{\\lambda}(ct - x)\\right]$, where $y$ and $x$ are measured in metres. Which of the following statements is true?</p>",
                    "options": [
                      {
                        "identifier": "A",
                        "content": "<p>The unit of $\\lambda$ is same as that of $x$ and $A$</p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "B",
                        "content": "<p>The unit of $\\lambda$ is same as that of $x$ but not of $A$</p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "C",
                        "content": "<p>The unit of $c$ is same as that of $\\frac{2\\pi}{\\lambda}$</p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "D",
                        "content": "<p>The unit of $(ct - x)$ is same as that of $\\frac{2\\pi}{\\lambda}$</p>"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "hi": {
                    "comprehension": null,
                    "direction": null,
                    "content": "<p>दिया गया है कि $y = A \\sin\\left[\\frac{2 \\pi}{\\lambda}(ct - x)\\right]$, जहाँ $y$ और $x$ मीटर में मापे जाते हैं। निम्नलिखित में से कौन सा कथन सत्य है?</p>",
                    "options": [
                      {
                        "identifier": "A",
                        "content": "<p>$\\lambda$ की इकाई $x$ और $A$ की इकाई के समान है</p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "B",
                        "content": "<p>$\\lambda$ की इकाई $x$ की इकाई के समान है परन्तु $A$ की नहीं</p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "C",
                        "content": "<p>$c$ की इकाई $\\frac{2\\pi}{\\lambda}$ की इकाई के समान है</p>"
                      },
                      {
                        "identifier": "D",
                        "content": "<p>$(ct - x)$ की इकाई $\\frac{2\\pi}{\\lambda}$ की इकाई के समान है</p>"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                },
                "subTopic": null,
                "subject": "physics",
                "timeAllotted": 90000,
                "topic": "unit-of-physical-quantities",
                "type": "mcq"
